<C>__{sofya}
<D>__{why can't my husband see you for what you are?}
<A>__{chertkov's face is red. he starts to speak, stops. he walks to the door, then very deliberately.}
<C>__{chertkov}
<D>__{if i had a wife like you, i would have blown my brains out long ago.}
<P>__{(beat)}
